Subject: Administrator sync between EPP and AD is not working. Manually creating a new user always pw error
Description: When I try to sync with the AD, no error message appears, and it claims that the synchronization is successful, but the new employees are not synchronized. I then tried to create the employee manually, but no matter what password I enter, it always returns an error stating that the password is incorrect.
Solution_Comment__c: Issue resolved by removing the admin and running the sink again.
